al Boxing Association.\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999039352626006, \"rank\": 9.607396679751444e-05, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9998239839545388, \"rank\": 0.00011437424699443559, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.121073141669697e-16, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini, who initially refused to shake hands with Khelif, said she didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t intend to disrespect the athlete.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999039352626006, \"rank\": 9.607396679751444e-05, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI want to apologize to her and everyone else.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was angry because my Olympics had gone up in smoke,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d shereportedlysaid, adding that she didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t agree with the transphobic discourse launched by the defeat.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sorry for my opponent, too.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the IOC said she can fight, I respect that decision.\\\"\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7597578132161963e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While former PresidentDonald Trump,VP nominee JD Vance, author JK Rowling, and the rest of the far-right transphobic internet swarm pushed unsubstantiated claims against Khelif, the IOC and others quickly quashed rumors that Khelif, who was born as a woman, was transgender.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 892, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999994842543367, \"rank\": 5.157456708690459e-07, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Pence\", \"score\": 0.9988205847040622, \"rank\": 0.0011782774759132044, \"text\": \"VP\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Pence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Pence\"}, {\"begin\": 909, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JD.com\", \"score\": 0.9358150280959797, \"rank\": 0.06764642361589648, \"text\": \"JD\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JD.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JD.com\"}, {\"begin\": 912, \